{"tid":1926595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王喜「驚方」暗寸謝Sir別有用心","createTime":"2020-03-15T08:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T09:42:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd37d6446c751c4a28999ce5720aeba594ceaea3","tid":1926595,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200315/NEQFODWYYIKL43GLI6E3SWRVN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200315%2FNEQFODWYYIKL43GLI6E3SWRVN4%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyRq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=46c5d330\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200315%2FNEQFODWYYIKL43GLI6E3SWRVN4%2F&h=cd6e198e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200315/NEQFODWYYIKL43GLI6E3SWRVN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n王喜「驚方」暗寸謝Sir別有用心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200315/large/1584192880_6f70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200315%2Flarge%2F1584192880_6f70.jpg&h=864ce4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜前晚主持的「驚方訊息」環節，以嬉笑怒罵的形式暗寸謝Sir的「別有用心」論。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n王喜為港台節目《頭條新聞》拍攝的「驚方訊息」前晚播出新一集，他甫現身就表示因被電視台拒絕播放關係，為要「扮」節省成本，故要將「驚方訊息」簡稱變為「驚訊」，而畫面的下半部亦即時「減成本」刪走一半。王喜在節目中指有些「別有用心」的人士發佈假新聞、假訊息等，畫面即跳到葵青警區指揮官謝振中早前在葵青區議會會議上的發言，王喜說：「呢一種不負責任行為，令到嗰啲特權人士，唔係，係特殊人士，即係欠缺常識又缺乏基礎理解能力嘅人信以為真，導致社會唔和諧。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【題材貼地】愛的單元探討社會現象<br />\n<br />\n其後，王喜在節目中討論到近年警隊嗜賭欠債問題，他反問︰「加薪加津貼會否令到欠債問題急速惡化？」王喜提到警方超時補水由2億多修訂為25億，將會令受武肺影響面臨倒閉的商店獲益：「相信呢25億，一定會用作本地消費、振興你哋嘅生意。」另外，王喜在節目播出前在社交網中留言，指委任證是警察在沒穿制服執法時，向其他人展示身份的證件，而不是犯法後獲得特赦的護身符。<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200315/large/1584192879_7781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200315%2Flarge%2F1584192879_7781.jpg&h=d306a70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在前晚的節目內，王喜探討近年警隊嗜賭及欠債問題。電視圖片"},{"pid":"05c6185f1ff06a6bb99ea698fed506bde5014775","tid":1926595,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"頭條新聞：第5集&mdash;大流行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926603</a>"},{"pid":"2bca645baff350aecf6dfe93e500c5591665e379","tid":1926595,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:22:54.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\nComment <br />\nLike<br />\nShare"},{"pid":"4028348f68cd18729762ac835de4e0e091c28542","tid":1926595,"uid":173844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"夠寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽得最多係休班警犯法 欠債 強姦<br />\n知法犯法先最垃圾"}]}